Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你一直的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  结果我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果  我还是无处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（对了她是有家不能回了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野君  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么  别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真没出息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真气人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好可爱  好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真气人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下班后能不能和我一起出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠  整天收拾不完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚、刚才走的是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我希望你明白一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得玄野君好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是...我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一会......我会收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出不了图像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  这个遥控器坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个旧货店大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没问题  肯定能收信号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么便宜的上哪儿去找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  出图像了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要调台  就自己动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经再也不想去那房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野  要不要一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日出台的CD店有签名会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多  简直是日本偶像大集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象是出版商办的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为靠着谁你才可以大摇大摆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到勒索时是谁救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去你自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发什么火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你不想跟我住  是想跟那家伙住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说过那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不说有区别么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再玩弄我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个混球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是查煤气的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么她也在  切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那不是北条政信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  这是多久前的演唱录像了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近没怎么见到他出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂志上登了  他从事务所退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成他死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪搅基社长的骚扰  自杀身死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问去日出台是在这候车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆闪开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去日出台...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  自己不会找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那时这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我找到站台了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在万分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉我要自己找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就努力地找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福  总算找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也多多加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不很确定  但它又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再去那个房间就能见到岸本了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的  不管那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点到那房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快传送啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  来了  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿计真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比小悟空和健四郎还厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从什么时候起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小步  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定...一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚看完预告部分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  大庭广众的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  又出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回是个COSPLAY狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群人怎么回事  全是陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位有什么疑问都可以问我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽我所知回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是啥子地方  啥人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单地说\N这里是通往极乐净土前的试炼之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说简单地说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可一点不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是往生极乐还是永堕地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者就聚集在此  在两者中决定去处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢看漫画是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  没什么  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依你说  我也死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可一点也不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该有死时的记忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承认自己已死的人是去不了极乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我记得电视上看到过这和尚）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（原来他死了）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（而且他恐怕认为死了也不坏呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（女人真少有）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本怎么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阿计
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（岸本可是更喜欢你的  气死了）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还有啊  你有问题就尽管问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿计  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说基什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  又跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这条狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和阿计一块儿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一块儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（别口不对心了）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤君  我、我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是吗  你别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们因不能接受自己的死亡而迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念经吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直念南无阿弥陀佛就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念的人就能往生极乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不念就永世不得超生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那个混混没出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你哪来的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再念什么佛也是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是和极乐什么的毫不相干的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的人也还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有许多事没干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能死！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是被召集来狩猎的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在还活着\N不同心协力是活不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经错乱了也是可以理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了  赶快念经！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  各位和我一起念南无阿弥陀佛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么变得有点滑稽  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也不管了  妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我果然还是想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这是前往极乐前的一站
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我怎么也想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个怎么看也是东京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间也和随便一栋楼里的布置一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看起来象而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的心跳还在  呼吸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵需要这些功能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是生前的记忆让你有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是御宅族吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢看动画？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么穿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对御宅什么的没偏见的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个年纪比我大不少的老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听他朋友说的  应该是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出现御宅族这个称呼前\N那些人是人们眼中的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约在七十年代末
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老哥是个电影狂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也因此结识了不少人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他对电影的事什么都知道  很有人望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从什么时候起  这种事成了笑料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种陈年旧事  我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是御宅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点象被甩的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别说些鼓励的话了  我不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我也不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人在胡扯什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球会唱歌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它唱的是电台的广播操歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会在电车上遇到这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心我扁你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要分心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的生命已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和尚  对不起  我比你清楚接下来要发生的事\N（新的早晨来临了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪来的歌声\N（充满希望的早晨）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  只是那房间里很无聊\N（满怀喜悦打开心扉仰望天空）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是你流泪的样子打动了我\N（随着收音机的节拍挺起胸膛）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（面对这扑面的春风吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（1、2、3）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么烦恼的事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就向御姐倾诉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我做...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我上床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人没出毛病吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你们的新生命怎么使用由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么一回事  什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生命...新生命是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说怎么使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的命它要怎么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来决定...这是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  插进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调皮星人？\N（调皮星人/捣蛋星人特征：强壮巨大）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么意思\N（喜欢的东西：狭窄处  乱发脾气）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是幕府将军吗？\N（口头禅：哼/哈）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那球差不多该打开了  小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都被你说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:20:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我  这边几个人也全都来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以关于游戏规则知道的稍微多点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快点换上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么突然就干起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我们已经死了  也很快乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  不要管她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都如同纯洁无暇的婴儿一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便遭遇困苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要放弃，勇敢向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在雨中我的心因往事而作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤寂的我犹如一块浮冰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻我纤弱的手指吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使我记起你的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:22:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便现在一切都结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的那个吻我永不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的吻，永不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损毁佛像是莫大的罪愆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此处非现世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦非来世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许毁佛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  我来干掉它
